{"tid":2060171,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"美國兩黨議員呼籲蓬佩奧接濟港人 要求聽日內交代方案","createTime":"2020-06-11T12:32:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-11T13:30:05.000Z","uid":305299,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"bd5f3d8eace9ddcaf67554be8f64230782bda19c","tid":2060171,"uid":305299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T12:32:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X5oyhZw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX5oyhZw.png&h=7a57bfbb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CRo2VLX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCRo2VLX.png&h=5c82031d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能我後知後覺，但原來前日9號，六位共和黨參議員加一位民主黨參議員，聯署去信國務卿蓬佩奧，呼籲提供渠道俾香港人生活喺北京獨裁管治之外，並建議同英國澳洲一齊合作，而且要求聽日12號收工之前向佢地俾個答覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n由9號到12號，前後四日，姑勿論蓬佩奧最後會俾咩答覆，試想像香港民選議員要求特區官員四日內俾個答覆，班高官會俾啲咩嘴臉出來<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但另外有一點值得留意，六四當日向國會提交港人庇護簽證法案嘅共和黨參議員Ben Sasse並唔係聯署人之一，所以可以話，實際上有起碼八位參議員支持接濟港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.young.senate.gov/imo/media/doc/20200609%20Young%20Letter%20to%20Secretary%20Pompeo%20re.%20Hong%20Kongers.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.young.senate.gov%2Fimo%2Fmedia%2Fdoc%2F20200609%2520Young%2520Letter%2520to%2520Secretary%2520Pompeo%2520re.%2520Hong%2520Kongers.pdf&d=isL%2BTa9V4QtjyiE8eWWd0h6eP3a%2FjAUraAi1lUB%2B7iI%3D&h=cf6ba8e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.young.senate.gov/imo/media/doc/20200609%20Young%20Letter%20to%20Secretary%20Pompeo%20re.%20Hong%20Kongers.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"ffcd72861634f08241ea257c8493b411b3ac4105","tid":2060171,"uid":51583,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T12:34:42.000Z","msg":"相信會有少量人可以走<br />\n但我都唔信幾個國家會肯全收港人<br />\n但點都好起碼要DQ一班建制/高官既人去<br />\n就算佢地已經有外國藉"},{"pid":"12ae70016882531e5048b3b2bdb779321411b799","tid":2060171,"uid":4661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T12:35:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c94034a3a8871ca62fa070f2de32e2dd212caea","tid":2060171,"uid":31215,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ffcd72861634f08241ea257c8493b411b3ac4105","tid":2060171,"uid":51583,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T12:34:42.000Z","msg":"相信會有少量人可以走<br />\n但我都唔信幾個國家會肯全收港人<br />\n但點都好起碼要DQ一班建制/高官既人去<br />\n就算佢地已經有外國藉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T12:40:16.000Z","msg":"我覺得咁情況分分鐘收留到過百萬港人<br />\n肯走就收<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7c59caf948576d5884226f6c8954aea9ff84b9f","tid":2060171,"uid":196445,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"7c94034a3a8871ca62fa070f2de32e2dd212caea","tid":2060171,"uid":31215,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ffcd72861634f08241ea257c8493b411b3ac4105","tid":2060171,"uid":51583,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T12:34:42.000Z","msg":"相信會有少量人可以走<br />\n但我都唔信幾個國家會肯全收港人<br />\n但點都好起碼要DQ一班建制/高官既人去<br />\n就算佢地已經有外國藉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T12:40:16.000Z","msg":"我覺得咁情況分分鐘收留到過百萬港人<br />\n肯走就收<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T12:41:53.000Z","msg":"基本上我覺得肯走就有機會，問題係香港有幾多人可以有能力或者適應到外國生活？"},{"pid":"b0dded50c1081543006c9988d1f96b90f81da318","tid":2060